{"tid":2143253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警涉改收禮指引 一萬變無上限  議員：黑箱審批得人驚","createTime":"2020-08-07T03:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T09:47:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28cb81d0173d8f7e6c932516c781bb73fa2b40c7","tid":2143253,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/UHK3XWKMSOLX572NCTBRBMB6UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FUHK3XWKMSOLX572NCTBRBMB6UA%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=4aba1ed7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FUHK3XWKMSOLX572NCTBRBMB6UA%2F&h=7e4b8c8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/UHK3XWKMSOLX572NCTBRBMB6UA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警涉改收禮指引 一萬變無上限 <br />\n議員：黑箱審批得人驚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fLNSrPgY3wYhP1NdCLGaWUFLPOE=/190x95/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EXEDLPAZUNKS2PMBYZMNPCGSFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfLNSrPgY3wYhP1NdCLGaWUFLPOE%3D%2F190x95%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEXEDLPAZUNKS2PMBYZMNPCGSFM.jpg&h=79e93c68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警隊屢被批評資源無限，近月仍常收到團體捐贈防疫物資。《警聲》圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港警屢被批評資源無限，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n網上討論區昨流傳數張相信是從電腦螢幕翻拍照片，顯示今年7月，警務處人事部紀律組發出標題「為改善公眾/人員利益而接受禮物」文件，指因應「踏浪者」及「松塔」行動，「從單一人士或機構接受價值逾港幣10,000元為改善利益的禮物及不論價值為改善人員利益的禮物」，各單位須按《程序手冊》要求送交警務處助理處長，再呈保安局或公務員事務局。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「保安局偏袒 難令人信服」<br />\n<br />\n文件說明個人保護裝備等禮物，如在行動中使用，可視為改善公眾利益；而零食及飲品等福利物品，被視為改善人員福利，前者如不超過一萬元，可由助理處長批核，逾一萬元則由保安局考慮；屬改善人員福利類別，不超過一萬元要由保安局批核，超過要由公務員事務局審批。<br />\n<br />\n本報去年10月曾報道，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l-cHMxP5h1yDWtPXSIAs0i1iE8g=/190x95/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PI5P6J2MZRX3BOJJPG64XNHUKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl-cHMxP5h1yDWtPXSIAs0i1iE8g%3D%2F190x95%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPI5P6J2MZRX3BOJJPG64XNHUKU.jpg&h=5751debb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上昨流傳文件，顯示參與「踏浪者」及「松塔」行動的警員可以「改善公眾利益」之名收取捐贈禮物。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷斥修訂「越嚟越得人驚」，「點可能無上限」，又指保安局雖有審批權，「大家都見保安局咁耐都偏袒警隊，點畀公眾信心係嚴格監管？」<br />\n<br />\n林更質疑廉署會否同意修訂，又指過去不時有藍絲團體及左派商人送禮，勢將加強公眾負面觀感和質疑，認為警方不應接受口罩、頭盔等物資，若裝備不符規格，會影響警員和市民。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科發言人回覆時未否認有關指引，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"5412435bb4651175005c2f5dab52c17e9bc93b3b","tid":2143253,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:12:22.000Z","msg":"扮都費事扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7943c8c9cd0c301ba62643702090bafcf052ffb","tid":2143253,"uid":185656,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbaAE8r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbaAE8r.png&h=5e369c47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61a8909184fb1176e16cb6395e6972e93d9203d0","tid":2143253,"uid":314611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"遲會唔會改警察強姦無罪<br />\n打劫無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0b1ddcb202834829a592d9808182ac152743d8","tid":2143253,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:40:47.000Z","msg":"我都唔明已經係政府部門咁多資源點解仲可以收禮<br />\n本身有權力已經好容易賄賂，仲要無上限"},{"pid":"5ccc711d062ba3642b679697b885730a64254d1c","tid":2143253,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.g